  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You transform the target&rsquo;s brain, allowing them to see sounds, hear scents, and otherwise perceive sensory input using multiple sensory organs. Even unusual senses, such as a @Compendium[sfrpg.races.VIJ6pdOVTJle3vJx]{Shirren}&rsquo;s vibration sense, are affected. For the duration of the spell, the target is immune to the @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.tOpF6qjnlnKc10t7]{Blinded}, dazzled, and @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.D8JvCEmOiWKe2UDx]{Deafened} conditions and gains a +2 enhancement bonus to Perception checks.</p>",
